                <h2 id="parent-3">Discounts and Promotions</h2><br>
                <h2 class="h2_height">Q: When should I refund?</h2>
                <p class="textcolor">
                    A: Common refund reasons include harassment, non-consensual recording, negative attitude,
                    and suspicious transactions. If you ever feel uncomfortable during an order, you should leave and
                    initiate a refund and report the incident to customer service by emailing support@epal.gg.
                    Note our refund window is 3 days after completion. Completed orders won’t be able to be refunded if they are more than three days old.
                </p><br>
                <h2 class="h2_height">Q: How can I remove a review?</h2>
                <p class="textcolor">
                    A: Due to consumer protection laws, reviews may only be removed if there is clear evidence of harassment or the order was never completed.
                    If a customer leaves a poor review that meets these requirements,
                    please email support@epal.gg. You can also contact the customer and issue a refund if needed, which will remove the review.
                </p><br>
                <h2 class="h2_height">Q: How can I review a customer?</h2>
                <p class="textcolor">
                    A: When an order is completed, navigate to the Order section and go to the “Completed” tab.
                    Click “Fast Review” to write an anonymous review for your customer - only other ePals can see customer reviews,
                    and customers cannot see their own reviews even if they are ePals.
                </p><br>
                <h2 id="parent-4">Refunds and Reviews</h2><br>
                <h2 class="h2_height">Q: How does the withdrawal period work exactly?</h2>
                <p class="textcolor">
                    A: When you have completed less than 20 paid orders, you can withdraw your Buff income after 15 days;
                </p><br>
                <p class="textcolor">
                    When you have completed 20 - 49 paid orders, you can withdraw your Buff income after 7 days;
                </p><br>
                <p class="textcolor">
                    Note: The money you earned before you advanced into the new tier will not be retroactively changed. They will still have the old and longer timer
                </p><br>

                <p class="textcolor">
